5205","canonical_id":"2606.25205","version_count":2,"previous_versions":["2606.25205"],"title":"A new $H_0$ measurement with SNe Requiem and Encore using Gravity.jl","authors":["L. Bazzanini","G. Di Rosa","A. Acebron","P. Bergamini","M. Lombardi","P. Rosati","G. Angora","G. B. Caminha","S. Ertl","G. Granata","A. M. Koekemoer","S. H. Suyu","J. Pierel","A. B. Newman","C. Grillo","S. Schuldt","M. Bulla","S. Cha","M. D'Addona","J. M. Diego","M. Fogliardi","B. L. Frye","M. J. Jee","P. S. Kamieneski","M. Meneghetti","A. Mercurio","E. Vanzella"],"categories":["astro-ph.CO","astro-ph.GA"],"summary":"本文利用新开发的贝叶斯参数透镜建模框架Gravity.jl，对星系团MACS J0138.0-2155进行强透镜分析，基于该团簇中两个多像Ia型超新星（SN Requiem和SN Encore）的观测数据，预测了它们未来的重现时间，并联合时间延迟测量约束哈勃常数H0=67.0_{-7.8}^{+9.3} km/s/Mpc。","date":"2026-06-25","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.25205","score":100,"stars":5,"tier":"recommended","mandatory":false,"score_breakdown":[{"label":"strong gravitational lensing","points":55},{"label":"gravitational lens modelling","points":28}],"must_read_reason":"","topics":["Strong Gravitational Lensing"]},{"id":"2606.30025","canonical_id":"2606.30025","version_count":1,"previous_versions":[],"title":"Probing Magnetic Fields In and Around Galaxies Near and Far","authors":["S. A. Mao","Rainer Beck","Aritra Basu","Lerato Baidoo","Andrea Bracco","Ralf-Jürgen Dettmar","Volker Hessen","Cathy Horellou","Timea O. Kovacs","Kohei Kurahara","Yu-Qing Lou","Yik Ki Ma","Rikuto Omae","Rosita Paladino","Amit Seta","Fatemeh Tabatabaei","Theresa Wiegert"],"categories":["astro-ph.GA"],"summary":"本文概述了利用SKA AA4进行星系磁场观测的科学目标与策略，包括对近邻星系的偏振巡天以及通过强引力透镜系统探测高红移星系磁场，以理解星系与磁场的共演化。","date":"2026-06-30","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.30025","score":95,"stars":5,"tier":"recommended","mandatory":false,"score_breakdown":[{"label":"strong gravitational lensing","points":55}],"must_read_reason":"","topics":["Strong Gravitational Lensing","Galaxy Evolution"]},{"id":"2606.23808","canonical_id":"2606.23808","version_count":2,"previous_versions":[